race.description: Tim Mccurdy Mp Ovens Valley Mdn Plate
race.comment: YOU SAID WHAT (7) is relatively lightly raced having gotten a long way back when 4 lengths from the winner in sixth over 1600m at Ballarat last start. Gets the switch to an inside gate here and finds a winnable maiden. PHANTOM'S CHASE (3) did enough fresh at Echuca over 1600m when battling home into sixth. Fitter for that now and can roll forward to offset the wide gate. Should take catching. JAPPALOUIS (2) had been going well prior to disappointing at Echuca last time, beaten a long way. Form prior gives him a genuine chance. IVE GOT THE POWER (6) will find this much easier than a race in town last time when outclassed.
